      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If the command contains any parameters other than line number or"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "label, SPF/PC assumes that it is the second format."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The operands NEXT, PREV, FIRST and LAST are used to control the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "direction of search:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- NEXT start at the cursor line and search forward"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- PREV start at the cursor line and search backward"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- FIRST start at the front of the file and search forward"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- LAST start at the end of the file and search backward"
      },
